article_title: Speculative Developers Take Medical Projects Off Back Burner
article_text:
Most developers in the medical-office-building business put speculative projects on hold during the recession.

Now some are revisiting the idea, breaking ground on new projects without having any tenants lined up.

Consider Downtown West Medical Offices, a medical-office-building project in central Los Angeles expected to be announced this...
